<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 04:09:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>愤怒、悲伤、沮丧：乔·拜登引发的白宫骚乱</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/rage-sadness-frustration-turmoil-in-the-white-house-over-joe-biden/articleshow/111446043.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111446043.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国总统乔·拜登周二承认，他在上周四的总统辩论中的表现并不是最好的，但将其归咎于六月初两次海外旅行后的时差反应。继上周不稳定的辩论表现后，拜登在 2024 年连任竞选中面临越来越多的质疑，一位众议院民主党同僚周二公开呼吁他退出竞选。周二晚上，拜登在弗吉尼亚州麦克莱恩举行的一场竞选活动上发表讲话，承认与他的共和党对手、前总统唐纳德·特朗普的辩论进行得并不顺利。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 03:24:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/rage-sadness-frustration-turmoil-in-the-white-house-over-joe-biden/articleshow/111446043.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国扣押台湾渔船 警告台湾不要干涉</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-seizes-taiwanese-fishing-boat-warns-taiwan-not-to-interfere/articleshow/111445540.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111445540.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;两名中国渔民死亡后，中国在金门附近持续进行海上执法，紧张局势加剧。赖清德总统任期内，来自中国的压力加大，促使台湾寻求沟通以释放被拘留的渔民。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 02:52:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-seizes-taiwanese-fishing-boat-warns-taiwan-not-to-interfere/articleshow/111445540.cms</guid></item><item><title>飓风 Beryl 造成 5 人死亡，强度降至 4 级，但仍然“极其危险”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hurricane-beryl-claims-5-lives-weakens-to-category-4-but-remains-extremely-dangerous/articleshow/111445652.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111445652.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 03:12:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hurricane-beryl-claims-5-lives-weakens-to-category-4-but-remains-extremely-dangerous/articleshow/111445652.cms</guid></item><item><title>与特朗普的辩论：拜登透露为什么他“在台上差点睡着”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/debate-with-trump-biden-reveals-why-he-nearly-fell-asleep-on-stage/articleshow/111445398.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111445398.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 02:56:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/debate-with-trump-biden-reveals-why-he-nearly-fell-asleep-on-stage/articleshow/111445398.cms</guid></item><item><title>飓风贝里尔正向牙买加袭来，威胁海地和多米尼加共和国</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hurricane-beryl-churning-toward-jamaica-threatens-haiti-and-dominican-republic/articleshow/111445096.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111445096.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;飓风贝丽尔为 4 级风暴，对牙买加、伊斯帕尼奥拉岛、海地太子港和开曼群岛构成威胁。拉尔夫·贡萨尔维斯总理报告联合岛遭受严重破坏。迪肯·米切尔总理强调了卡里亚库和小马提尼克岛遭受的破坏。科学家克里斯托弗·罗佐夫将贝里尔的快速增强归因于北大西洋的高温。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 02:19:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hurricane-beryl-churning-toward-jamaica-threatens-haiti-and-dominican-republic/articleshow/111445096.cms</guid></item><item><title>鲍里斯·约翰逊出人意料地为避免保守党被淘汰而做出了迟到的举动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-polls-boris-johnson-rishi-sunak-conservative-party-labour-party/articleshow/111445606.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111445606.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;鲍里斯·约翰逊周二晚出人意料地露面，敦促保守党选民阻止工党在即将到来的英国大选中取得压倒性胜利。在伦敦市中心的一次计划外演讲中，约翰逊并未以保守党候选人身份参选，他警告说，获得绝大多数席位的工党政府将抹杀保守党取得的成就。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 02:59:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-polls-boris-johnson-rishi-sunak-conservative-party-labour-party/articleshow/111445606.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国正在为俄罗斯建造和测试致命攻击无人机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-is-building-and-testing-lethal-attack-drones-for-russia/articleshow/111445416.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111445416.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据欧洲官员称，中国和俄罗斯公司正在开发一种类似于伊朗沙赫德型号的攻击无人机，该型号已在乌克兰使用。这项合作于 2023 年开始，目前已进入开发和测试阶段，旨在将无人机运送到俄罗斯。中国无人机尚未在乌克兰部署。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 02:55:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-is-building-and-testing-lethal-attack-drones-for-russia/articleshow/111445416.cms</guid></item><item><title>海上无人机袭击后，俄罗斯新罗西斯克当局限制海滩进入</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russias-novorossiysk-authorities-limit-beach-access-after-sea-drones-attacks/articleshow/111445322.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111445322.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯经常指责乌克兰袭击其黑海沿岸和莫斯科吞并的克里米亚半岛的港口城市，但俄罗斯官员往往不会透露乌克兰袭击造成的全部损失。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 02:35:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russias-novorossiysk-authorities-limit-beach-access-after-sea-drones-attacks/articleshow/111445322.cms</guid></item><item><title>马来西亚法院驳回被监禁的前总理纳吉布软禁服刑的申请</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/malaysia-court-dismisses-jailed-ex-pm-najibs-bid-to-serve-sentence-under-house-arrest/articleshow/111445095.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111445095.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;前总理纳吉布·拉扎克 (Najib Razak) 的软禁申请被马来西亚法院驳回，推动执行 1MDB 丑闻案件中的皇家命令。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 02:19:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/malaysia-court-dismisses-jailed-ex-pm-najibs-bid-to-serve-sentence-under-house-arrest/articleshow/111445095.cms</guid></item><item><title>民调：哈里斯在美国总统选举中比拜登更有机会</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-presidential-elections-kamala-harris-has-better-chance-than-biden-within-close-range-of-trump-claims-poll/articleshow/111444881.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111444881.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 01:57:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-presidential-elections-kamala-harris-has-better-chance-than-biden-within-close-range-of-trump-claims-poll/articleshow/111444881.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度工人在意大利农场发生事故失血过多身亡 地主被捕</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/indian-worker-bleeds-to-death-in-accident-on-italian-farm-landowner-arrested/articleshow/111444846.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111444846.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 02:17:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/indian-worker-bleeds-to-death-in-accident-on-italian-farm-landowner-arrested/articleshow/111444846.cms</guid></item><item><title>海地总理誓言对受帮派伤害的民众“透明”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/haiti-pm-vows-transparency-to-population-traumatized-by-gangs/articleshow/111444851.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111444851.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加里·科尼尔重新担任海地总理，承诺在帮派暴力和基础设施崩溃的情况下保持透明度和合作。拥有联合国背景的他在国际支持下专注于眼前的安全，同时加强当地警察的力量。科尼尔的目标是在 2026 年之前重建信任、解决危机并组织选举，强调透明度和结构化进展，以实现成功过渡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 01:54:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/haiti-pm-vows-transparency-to-population-traumatized-by-gangs/articleshow/111444851.cms</guid></item><item><title>拆除德克萨斯州教堂的计划吸引游客返回避难所</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/plans-to-demolish-texas-church-where-gunman-opened-fire-in-2017-draw-visitors-back-to-sanctuary/articleshow/111444576.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111444576.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 01:20:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/plans-to-demolish-texas-church-where-gunman-opened-fire-in-2017-draw-visitors-back-to-sanctuary/articleshow/111444576.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登提出新规则以保护工人免受酷热影响</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-moots-new-rule-to-safeguard-workers-from-extreme-heat/articleshow/111440764.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111440764.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 21:30:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-moots-new-rule-to-safeguard-workers-from-extreme-heat/articleshow/111440764.cms</guid></item><item><title>加利福尼亚州和美国中南部出现危险的高温</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/dangerously-high-heat-builds-in-california-and-the-south-central-united-states/articleshow/111440439.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111440439.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 19:49:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/dangerously-high-heat-builds-in-california-and-the-south-central-united-states/articleshow/111440439.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦猛烈抨击联合国机构报告，称逮捕伊姆兰是“任意的、出于政治动机”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-slams-un-body-report-calling-imrans-arrest-arbitrary-politically-motivated/articleshow/111440399.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111440399.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 19:45:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-slams-un-body-report-calling-imrans-arrest-arbitrary-politically-motivated/articleshow/111440399.cms</guid></item><item><title>刺杀萨尔曼·拉什迪的凶手拒绝涉及恐怖主义指控的认罪协议，刑期较轻</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/salman-rushdies-stabber-rejects-plea-deal-involving-terrorism-charge-with-lesser-jail-term/articleshow/111439008.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111439008.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 26 岁的哈迪·马塔尔 (Hadi Matar) 被控在 2022 年刺伤作家萨尔曼·拉什迪 (Salman Rushdie)，他的律师纳撒尼尔 (Nathaniel) 表示，他周二拒绝了认罪协议，该协议可以降低他在州监狱的刑期，但可能会导致联邦恐怖主义相关指控巴罗内.袭击发生后，马塔尔仍被拘留，不得保释。拉什迪正准备在纽约西部的肖托夸机构发表演讲。拉什迪受了重伤，其中一只眼睛失明，还有十几处刀伤。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 17:32:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/salman-rushdies-stabber-rejects-plea-deal-involving-terrorism-charge-with-lesser-jail-term/articleshow/111439008.cms</guid></item><item><title>国防部长奥斯汀表示，美国将宣布向乌克兰提供价值超过23亿美元的武器包</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-to-announce-over-2-3-billion-arms-package-for-ukraine-says-defense-secretary-austin/articleshow/111438739.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111438739.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国正准备宣布向乌克兰提供价值超过23亿美元的新安全援助计划。国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀在五角大楼与乌克兰国防部长会面时透露了这一点。该计划是为了回应乌克兰官员因俄罗斯军队频繁发动导弹和无人机袭击而不断呼吁增加防空系统的呼声。新的一揽子计划预计将包括反坦克武器、防空拦截器以及快速采购NASAMS和爱国者防空拦截器。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-to-announce-over-2-3-billion-arms-package-for-ukraine-says-defense-secretary-austin/articleshow/111438739.cms</guid></item><item><title>200名候选人退出法国民意调查以阻止极右翼获胜前景</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/200-candidates-withdraw-from-french-poll-to-block-far-rights-win-prospect/articleshow/111435404.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111435404.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据法新社报道，至少有 200 名候选人退出法国大选，以阻止极右翼政党掌权，旨在防止反右派选票分裂。马琳·勒庞领导的共和党在周日提前选举的第一轮选举中成为领跑者，超过了总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的中间派阵营，该阵营在左翼联盟之后排名第三。马克龙提前举行大选的决定似乎适得其反。 RN 反对欧盟进一步一体化的立场及其减少对欧盟资助的计划引起了人们的担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 14:29:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/200-candidates-withdraw-from-french-poll-to-block-far-rights-win-prospect/articleshow/111435404.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度侨民会在英国民意调查中支持里希·苏纳克吗？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/will-indian-diaspora-back-rishi-sunak-in-uk-polls/articleshow/111437208.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111437208.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;总理里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)在为期六周的竞选活动中穿越全国时常常显得疲惫不堪，周四投票前的倒数第二天，他在伦敦北部卢顿的一个巨大的奥卡多仓库里开始了竞选活动，看着机器人挑选要运送的物品。苏纳克比预期提前几个月举行选举，令党内和全国许多人感到震惊。他经历了一场艰难的竞选活动，面临着选民和记者的质疑，为什么国家的状况没有好转。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 14:32:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/will-indian-diaspora-back-rishi-sunak-in-uk-polls/articleshow/111437208.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>